         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">5/6/94. ¶  ¶ It is with feelings of great sadness, dear Madam, that I hear of your severe bereavement through the english telegrams. In offering my profound condolence to you and your children, I feel...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.06.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edith Pearson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>MS 7420, Box 440/4(a), La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>5/6/94.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is with feelings of great sadness, dear Madam, that I hear of your severe bereavement through the english telegrams. In offering my profound condolence to you and your children, I feel, that I should express once more my indebtedness for the enlightened interest and generous support, evinced by the late Dr Pearson<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles Henry Pearson died in London on 29 May 1894.</p>
               </note> in and for my scientific and official career, and this will be borne with grateful sentiments ever in my remembrance.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With deep sympathy</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
